data_created: contains data generate through Python-scripts or QGIS operations\
allergenenicty_final_map: contains all elements necessary to produce the final map shown in the final map paper\
allergenetic_index: contains the .csv of all assigned allergenicity scores\
descriptive_statistics: contains charts generated by 02_descriptive_statistics.py\
visualisations: contains visualisations made with Adobe Illustrator\
\
