# 2. Order of execution\
\
1. Execute 01_data_formatting.py\
2. Execute 02_descriptive_statistics.py\
3. Execute 03_buffer_analysis.py\
4. Rasterize genera buffers and summarize rasters in QGIS\
5. Execute buffer_descriptive.py\
6. Vectorise produced allergenicity pressure map in QGIS\
7. Calculate weight matrix Moran\'92s I in GeoDa\
\
